{
  "id": "adv_event_2202_01_05",
  "title": "LizNoirのバレンタイン",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_05-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "この衣装、いいね。僕は気に入ったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I like this outfit. It suits my taste.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 4.959546423,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 5.1462129753
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_05-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "ですよね～。デザイナーさんがこころのイメージを\nパーフェクトに表現してくれました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes~ The designer perfectly\nexpressed Kokoro's image.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.1462129753,
      "endTime": 11.5571424645,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 11.7638090929
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_05-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "それにしても、あれから企画をもう一度練り直して\nよく間に合わせられたわね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But still‚ we had to rework the concept from scratch.\nWe barely made it in time…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.7638090929,
      "endTime": 17.9998180231,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_05-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　あの後、こころともう一度、考え直したんです\nヒントが、すぐそばにあったんですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes! After that‚ Kokoro and I rethought everything.\nThe hint was right there‚ close by.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.1864848615,
      "endTime": 25.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 25.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_05-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "ん？　それは何？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hm? What was it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.8,
      "endTime": 28.0389796257,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_05-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さんが、愛に渡した差し入れです\nあのプリンが……ヒントになったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio-san gave it to Ai as a treat.\nThat pudding… it became a hint.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.2333333333,
      "endTime": 34.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_05-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "あれを一口食べた時、ビビッときたんです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I took a bite‚ it just clicked!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.2666666667,
      "endTime": 38.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 38.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_05-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "何か特別なプリンだったの？　莉央",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Was it some special pudding? Rio?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.5333333333,
      "endTime": 41.6912244161,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_05-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "いいえ、美味しいけど\nごく普通のプリンじゃなかったかしら……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ it was delicious‚ but just a regular pudding…\nWasn't anything special about it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.9,
      "endTime": 46.501783815900005,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_05-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "それがなんのヒントになったの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ what was the hint?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.7,
      "endTime": 48.8760091066,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 49.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_05-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "ヒントになったのは、プリンじゃなくて\nプリンにかかっているカラメルソースの方です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The hint wasn't the pudding itself.\nIt was the caramel sauce on top of the pudding.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.0666666667,
      "endTime": 54.8400000205,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 55.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_05-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "プリンって、甘いスイーツって印象が強いですけど\nカラメルソースって、苦味もあるじゃないですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Puddings are usually associated with sweetness‚\nbut caramel sauce has a bitter taste‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.0333333333,
      "endTime": 61.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_05-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "あれだけのヒントで気付いてしまうなんて\nこころは……こころは自分の才能が恐ろしい……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To notice that hint with just that much‚\nKokoro… Kokoro's talent is frightening…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.1666666667,
      "endTime": 70.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 70.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_05-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "冗談はもういいから、話を進めてくれない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Enough with the jokes. Can you continue with the story?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.5333333333,
      "endTime": 73.9852834542,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 74.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_05-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "そうね。続きを聞かせてちょうだい\nカラメルソースが、なんのヒントになったの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right. Please continue.\nHow did the caramel sauce become a hint?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.2,
      "endTime": 80.516756746,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 80.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_05-kkr007.m4a",
      "text": "甘いだけが正義じゃない\nほろ苦いバレンタインでもいいんだってことです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sweetness isn't the only definition of goodness.\nEven a bittersweet Valentine's is fine!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.7,
      "endTime": 86.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_05-kkr008.m4a",
      "text": "それで『ビターチョコ、苦い恋、切ないバレンタイン』\nというキーワードが生まれたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's how \"Bitter Chocolate‚ Bitter Love‚ Melancholic Valentine\"\nthose keywords were born.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.8333333333,
      "endTime": 94.03333333329999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 94.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_05-kkr009.m4a",
      "text": "まあ、ヒントはそれだけじゃなかったんですけど……\n……とにかくどうです？　この天才的ひらめきは～？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ the hint wasn't just that…\nAnyway‚ what do you think? Isn't this a genius inspiration~?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.2333333333,
      "endTime": 103,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_05-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "思ってたより単純だったね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It turned out simpler than I thought.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.2,
      "endTime": 105.6778683662,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 105.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_05-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "そうね。単純。……でも、だからこそ\n力強いテーマになったんじゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ simple… But that's why\nit became a powerful theme‚ didn't it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.8666666667,
      "endTime": 112.6964805371,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 112.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_05-kkr010.m4a",
      "text": "単純、単純って……心外です～\nもっとこう、神を崇めるような反応を期待してたのに～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Simple‚ simple… It's disappointing~\nI was expecting a more worshipful reaction~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.9,
      "endTime": 122.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 122.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_05-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "ははっ、そうだね。凄い凄い。頑張ったね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haha‚ yeah. Amazing‚ amazing. You did well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.7666666667,
      "endTime": 128.6262584369,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 128.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_05-kkr011.m4a",
      "text": "チョコは甘いもの、バレンタインは楽しい行事っていう\n固定概念を破って企画を生み出したんですよ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chocolates are sweet‚ and Valentine's is a joyful event‚\nbut we broke free from those fixed notions and came up with a plan‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.8333333333,
      "endTime": 136.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_05-kkr012.m4a",
      "text": "大偉業を成し遂げたと言ってもいいはずですう\nなのにも～、なんですかその態度は～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We can even say we achieved something great!\nAnd yet… What's with that attitude?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.1333333333,
      "endTime": 143.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
